collectible.name: AlottaTrash
collectible.author: 0x7b511800a8d8e7de24dd19de3103081824b6f41d
collectible.description: AlottaTrash is an homage to the legendary artist and voxel architect, Alotta Money.  This design is inspired by Alotta Money’s voxel creation from Epoch 1 (32X32 #6, The Silly Vox).  Peeping out and incorporated into the can, is a Silly Vox inspired character, the handles are Silly Vox style hands and the lid is a bowler hat.  RIP #AlottaLove
